          <div class="layout_2">
            <h3>ParisTech Shanghai Jiao Tong</h3>
<p><a href="http://speit.sjtu.edu.cn/indexen.html">SJTU-ParisTech Elite Institute of Technology (SPEIT)</a> is established under the cooperation of Shanghai Jiao Tong University and Paris Tech. The establishment of this institute is an important action of Shanghai Jiao Tong University by implementing the &ldquo;Elite Engineer Cultivation Plan&rdquo; advocated by China&rsquo;s ministry of education. In April, 2012, the signing ceremony of SJTU-ParisTech cooperation agreement was held to establish a college of engineering. And also under the support of the Minhang area government and Zizhu Science-based Industrial Park, in the future the school will be relocated to Zizhu Science-based Industrial Park in International Education Center, where the college will be provided with teaching building, scientific and research and management room of 30,000 square meters, while supporting the supply of students&rsquo; apartments, foreign experts&rsquo; apartments as well as recreational and sports facilities, etc.</p>
<p>About the education mode, SPEIT utilizes the French elite engineer education mode with the schooling lasting 6 to 6.5 years. Most of the courses are taught in French, some in English or Chinese. For students in our college, they should, on the first stage, learn French and study the science-oriented basic courses by referring to the preparatory course teaching system in France; and on the second stage, focus on the comprehensive science coursework and major courses; and the on the third stage, accomplish the study of the whole major courses as well as dissertation writing. Currently, SPEIT consists of 3 major disciplines, including Mechanical Engineering and Automation, Information Engineering and Thermal Energy and Power Engineering. After fulfilling the academic requirements, students in our college can get bachelor's degree certificate and undergraduate course graduation certificate of Shanghai Jiao Tong University, postgraduate course graduation certificate and master degree of engineering of Shanghai Jiao Tong University, and the SPEIT engineer diploma authorized by CTI.</p>
<p>About the faculty, SPEIT makes the best of education resources of Paris Tech. Preparatory teachers and most professional course teachers are appointed by ParisTech, excellent teachers with oversea education background in SJTU and business specialists closely cooperated with our college are also appointed to teaching some courses; which are committed to cultivating outstanding engineers and business leaders with international vision, comprehend competiveness and applied orientation, to fit in with the needs of economic and social development of our country.  SPEIT&rsquo;s top management, called joint administrative committee, is composed of members from SJTU, ParisTech and chinese-foreign cooperative enterprises. Meanwhile, other two steering committees Academic Council and Scientific Committee have been established, providing suggestion and decision support for education and teaching, science and technology, school-enterprise cooperation and the development of the college. Management decision of joint administrative committee is carried out by the Chinese dean and the French dean respectively according to their own responsibility. And also, the joint administrative committee is equipped with two deputy deans, who are respectively responsible for the teaching and administrative work. At the same time, the college has established the administrative office, academic affairs office and student affairs office, which contribute to dealing with all kinds of management work of the college. SPEIT attaches great importance to the cooperation with business community. With the establishment of the enterprise club and the close relation to business community, it aims at developing cooperation with business community on talents cultivation as well as scientific and technological research.</p>
<p>For more information about ParisTech Shanghai Jiao Tong, please visit <a href="http://speit.sjtu.edu.cn/indexen.html">http://speit.sjtu.edu.cn/indexen.html</a>.</p>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Engineering</h3>
<p>Our UM-SJTU <a href="/admission/joint-institute/">Jiont Institute</a> offers students a chance to study in an English-language environment for Undergraduate Degree, Graduate Degree, Dual Degree Program (2+2) in which students may apply for transfer to the University of Michigan in their sophomore year and Combined Undergraduate/Graduate Program (CUGP) for students seeking Master&rsquo;s and PhD degrees from the University of Michigan.</p>
<ul class="blue_arrow">
<li><a href="http://umji.sjtu.edu.cn/News_View/?NewsID=2185" target="_blank">JI Undergraduate Degree Program</a></li>
<li><a href="http://umji.sjtu.edu.cn/News_View/?NewsID=2980" target="_blank">JI Graduate Degree Program</a></li>
<li> <a href="http://umji.sjtu.edu.cn/News_View/?NewsID=2186" target="_blank">UM-SJTU Dual Degree Program</a></li>
<li><a href="http://umji.sjtu.edu.cn/News_View/?NewsID=2187" target="_blank">UM-SJTU Combined Undergraduate / Graduate Program (CUGP)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://umji.sjtu.edu.cn/News_View/?NewsID=2228" target="_blank">Summer Programs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://umji.sjtu.edu.cn/News_View/?NewsID=2188" target="_blank">Q&amp;A</a></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Economics and Management</h3>
<p>As the only business school in Chinese Mainland triple-accredited by AACSB, EQUIS and AMBA, <a href="http://www.acem.sjtu.edu.cn/en/" target="_blank">the Antai College of Economics &amp; Management (ACEM)</a>, Shanghai Jiao Tong University, aims to develop the highest-level managerial talent, with fully international viewpoints and capabilities, and the ability to compete in the global economy. While focusing on academic research, the College is also committed to serving national and international corporations and institutions, through leading-edge consulting and research. Already a top-ranked college in China, ACEM strives to be recognized as a top economics and management college in Asia, with a worldwide reputation.  For the international programs, the college complies continuously with international practices pertaining to program portfolios, curriculum design and innovations. Antai has built up international cooperative networks at various levels, to provide high-quality English programs to international students. We currently have English Programs like: Antai Global Summer School, International MBA program, Joint venture Programs, and other student exchange programs.</p>
<ul class="blue_arrow">
<li><a href="http://www.summerschool.sjtu.edu.cn/" target="_blank">Antai Global Summer School</a><br />
<p>Have you been considering how should you spend your next summer? How about Learning about China&nbsp;and&nbsp;differentiating yourself from the crowd, and making the best of your summer with Antai Global Summer School?&nbsp;The 2013&nbsp;Antai Global Summer School is opening&nbsp;for application now.&nbsp;We welcome you to&nbsp;join students from all over the world in Shanghai for a truly exciting experience!</p>
<p>The Antai Global Summer School is an&nbsp;elaborate&nbsp;and internationalized&nbsp;program&nbsp;of Antai College of Economics and Management, Shanghai Jiao Tong University (SJTU),&nbsp;which will take place from July1<sup>st</sup>&nbsp;to July&nbsp;19<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;at 2013&nbsp;summer. The program will be worth 3&nbsp;SJTU&nbsp;credits/9 ECTS credits, full-time, and English-based. Students can have the credits transferred officially from our college to theirs. The program's general theme will be "Business and Culture in China", which will cover three interesting sub-themes during the three weeks: "Chinese Economics and Culture", "Consumer Behaviors and HR Management in China", and "Marketing and Strategies of Chinese Companies". Furthermore, "Surviving Chinese" language lessons, company visits, and rich sightseeing and cultural activities will be integrated into the program as well. Although it is an open-enrollment program, we encourage our partners with exchange agreements with our college to send your students on an exchange basis - which will allow the tuition fee to be waived for each applicant.</p>
<p>Prospective students of the program can contact Ms.&nbsp;Ginger XU, Senior Manager in&nbsp;Summer Schoolat our International Cooperation and Exchange Office to receive more information, by phone: +86-21-52302509, email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:iceo@sjtu.edu.cn">iceo@sjtu.edu.cn</a>, or the program website:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.summerschool.sjtu.edu.cn/">www.summerschool.sjtu.edu.cn</a>&nbsp;The application kit can be downloaded from the site, as well.</p>
<p>We look forward to welcoming you to Shanghai, and to welcoming you to Shanghai Jiao Tong University<span style="font-size: 10px;">.</span></p>
</li>
<li><a href="http://mba.acemsjtu.com/index.php/enindex/" target="_blank">International MBA Program</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.acem.sjtu.edu.cn/en/intl/intl_program.jsp" target="_blank">Joint Venture Programs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.acem.sjtu.edu.cn/en/intl/p_institutions.jsp" target="_blank">Student exchange</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.acem.sjtu.edu.cn/en/mas/news/3265.html" target="_blank">The Master Program of Management and Business (MMB)</a></li>
</ul>
