<h3>Finance</h3>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="vertical-align:top;"><img style="float:left; margin-right:5px;" src="/assets/449/SAIFlogo_normal.jpg" alt="SAIF" width="73" height="120" /></td>
<td><a href="http://www.saif.sjtu.edu.cn/en/">Shanghai Advanced Institute of Finance (SAIF)</a>, the first business school in Asia with a distinct finance focus, was established with strategic and financial support from the Shanghai Municipal Government. SAIF is committed to educating top finance professionals by virtue of its world-class facilities and internationally acclaimed faculty that consists largely of tenured professors from top universities in North America. We currently offer the following English programs:              
<ul class="blue_arrow">
<li><a href="http://www.saif.sjtu.edu.cn/mba/en/" target="_blank">Finance MBA</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.saif.sjtu.edu.cn/master/en/" target="_blank">Master of Finance</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.saif.sjtu.edu.cn/doctor/en/" target="_blank">PhD in Finance</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
